ğŸŸ¨ Jenkinsfile Is Stored in Git

The Jenkinsfile goes into the root of your repository:

my-app/
  â”œâ”€â”€ src/
  â”œâ”€â”€ pom.xml
  â””â”€â”€ Jenkinsfile


Jenkins automatically scans GitHub and finds the Jenkinsfile.

